Member 2: Data and AI Lead
Design and compute link-health features such as heartbeat interval, missed heartbeats, latency, jitter, and dropout streaks to measure signal degradation. Develop the first prediction model, starting with a rule-based risk score and then possibly a lightweight classifier (depending on difficulty and time).
